text: Boubout Dieng (born 19 November 1961) is a Mauritanian Olympic sprinter. Dieng competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics held in Barcelona. He entered the 200 metres and he finished 7th in his heat in a time of 22.75 seconds but didn't advance to the next round. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic athletes of Mauritania Category:Mauritanian male sprinters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1992 Summer Olympics
